  "difficultyLevel": 4,
  "lyrics": "Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh\nCan you feel that dream alive again?\nOh yeah, I don't know what it takes here\nHave you been what I know, there?\nAre you here for me forever?\nAre you dreaming real?\nBut my dreams, they are coming in night\nMakes me know what's right\nMakes me wanna be everything\nto you again our dreams yeah\nI got more of them here\nInside of me, you'll hear\nI'm all about it yeah all the time\nAnd I got these dreams I know that I fight\nI don't know if they're right\nWhen you know that you're right there\nDreaming with me\nThese just dreams that you don't know\nI said all day, all day, healing\nTill it gets, till it gets feeling\nOh, these dreams keep me up at night\nThese wants make me wanna fight off\nAn intellectual part of me\nI said these dreams keep me up at night\nThese hearts always take me the wrong way\nHard way, every which way\nBut my own is some semblance of whats on my mind\nAnd I don't wanna think about all the times\nThat I broke your heart\nAnd took your dreams away, baby\nBut I know these dreams are sticking with me\nAnd another chance and we'll be\nWhat we want to see, oh baby\nThese dreams, they be coming up right\nYeah, they be making me fight\nYeah, they be making me fuck my life up all the way\nBut I know that you can dream with me\nA little brighter and be more than we see\nCome on now, be more than you ever thought could be\nWith these dreams in your night\nYeah, these dreams, they fight you\nBut do they haunt you?\nOr do they just make you start at the beginning again?\nIs it that bad to get to experiment\nthe experiences of being part of being that of being everything\nAnd I know that these dreams, they come at night\nI don't care, I'm not scared anymore\nOf what you'll say to my only thoughts\nJust know that I am coming inside\nto slay another lock\nTo write another book\nDo you wanna sing on the hook?\nBaby, with my dreams at night\nYou know I rock this shit all right\nNo fighting, fussing, fuck the fighting, yeah\nYou know",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 7,
      "text": "Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh",
      "start": 1.159999966621399
    },
    {
      "end": 11.140000343322754,
      "text": "Can you feel that dream alive again?",
      "start": 8.300000190734863
    },
    {
      "end": 15.65999984741211,
      "text": "Oh yeah, I don't know what it takes here",
      "start": 11.579999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 18.559999465942383,
      "text": "Have you been what I know, there?",
      "start": 15.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 21.200000762939453,
      "text": "Are you here for me forever?",
      "start": 18.739999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 22.780000686645508,
      "text": "Are you dreaming real?",
      "start": 21.420000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 26.440000534057617,
      "text": "But my dreams, they are coming in night",
      "start": 22.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 29.559999465942383,
      "text": "Makes me know what's right",
      "start": 27.100000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 32.439998626708984,
      "text": "Makes me wanna be everything",
      "start": 29.559999465942383
    },
    {
      "end": 35.560001373291016,
      "text": "to you again our dreams yeah",
      "start": 32.47999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 37.560001373291016,
      "text": "I got more of them here",
      "start": 36.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 41.939998626708984,
      "text": "Inside of me, you'll hear",
      "start": 38.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 45.779998779296875,
      "text": "I'm all about it yeah all the time",
      "start": 42.380001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 49.81999969482422,
      "text": "And I got these dreams I know that I fight",
      "start": 45.779998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 52.560001373291016,
      "text": "I don't know if they're right",
      "start": 49.939998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 55.560001373291016,
      "text": "When you know that you're right there",
      "start": 53.119998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 57.86000061035156,
      "text": "Dreaming with me",
      "start": 56.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 60.119998931884766,
      "text": "These just dreams that you don't know",
      "start": 57.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 62.97999954223633,
      "text": "I said all day, all day, healing",
      "start": 60.119998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 68.9000015258789,
      "text": "Till it gets, till it gets feeling",
      "start": 63.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 72.27999877929688,
      "text": "Oh, these dreams keep me up at night",
      "start": 68.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 76.69999694824219,
      "text": "These wants make me wanna fight off",
      "start": 72.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 80.41999816894531,
      "text": "An intellectual part of me",
      "start": 77.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 83.87999725341797,
      "text": "I said these dreams keep me up at night",
      "start": 80.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 87.41999816894531,
      "text": "These hearts always take me the wrong way",
      "start": 83.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 89.27999877929688,
      "text": "Hard way, every which way",
      "start": 87.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 93.81999969482422,
      "text": "But my own is some semblance of whats on my mind",
      "start": 89.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 96.86000061035156,
      "text": "And I don't wanna think about all the times",
      "start": 93.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 98.87999725341797,
      "text": "That I broke your heart",
      "start": 96.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 103.63999938964844,
      "text": "And took your dreams away, baby",
      "start": 100.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 107.5,
      "text": "But I know these dreams are sticking with me",
      "start": 103.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 110.36000061035156,
      "text": "And another chance and we'll be",
      "start": 107.5
    },
    {
      "end": 115.26000213623047,
      "text": "What we want to see, oh baby",
      "start": 111.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 119.31999969482422,
      "text": "These dreams, they be coming up right",
      "start": 115.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 122.18000030517578,
      "text": "Yeah, they be making me fight",
      "start": 119.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 126.73999786376953,
      "text": "Yeah, they be making me fuck my life up all the way",
      "start": 122.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 129.5800018310547,
      "text": "But I know that you can dream with me",
      "start": 126.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 133.66000366210938,
      "text": "A little brighter and be more than we see",
      "start": 129.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 139.16000366210938,
      "text": "Come on now, be more than you ever thought could be",
      "start": 134.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 142.17999267578125,
      "text": "With these dreams in your night",
      "start": 139.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 146.36000061035156,
      "text": "Yeah, these dreams, they fight you",
      "start": 142.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 148.94000244140625,
      "text": "But do they haunt you?",
      "start": 146.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 152.8800048828125,
      "text": "Or do they just make you start at the beginning again?",
      "start": 149.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 157.52000427246094,
      "text": "Is it that bad to get to experiment",
      "start": 153
    },
    {
      "end": 161.63999938964844,
      "text": "the experiences of being part of being that of being everything",
      "start": 157.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 164.75999450683594,
      "text": "And I know that these dreams, they come at night",
      "start": 161.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 168.0800018310547,
      "text": "I don't care, I'm not scared anymore",
      "start": 164.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 173.9199981689453,
      "text": "Of what you'll say to my only thoughts",
      "start": 169.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 177.52000427246094,
      "text": "Just know that I am coming inside",
      "start": 173.9199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 179.9199981689453,
      "text": "to slay another lock",
      "start": 178
    },
    {
      "end": 182.75999450683594,
      "text": "To write another book",
      "start": 180.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 185.77999877929688,
      "text": "Do you wanna sing on the hook?",
      "start": 183.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 187.36000061035156,
      "text": "Baby, with my dreams at night",
      "start": 185.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 191.16000366210938,
      "text": "You know I rock this shit all right",
      "start": 187.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 196.9600067138672,
      "text": "No fighting, fussing, fuck the fighting, yeah",
      "start": 192.89999389648438
